.space-y-10
  %section
    %p.text-sm.font-semibold.uppercase.tracking-wide.text-sky-700.dark:text-sky-300 User Management Service
    %h1.mt-2.text-3xl.font-bold Demo Links
    %p.mt-3.max-w-3xl.text-gray-700.dark:text-gray-300
      Stable fixture queries for timing runs, cache checks, and Jaeger trace inspection. These links use host-facing development ports.

  %section
    %h2.text-xl.font-semibold Random Explorer
    %p.mt-2.text-sm.text-gray-600.dark:text-gray-300
      Pick a live organization, discover its admin through native grants, then inspect account and user counts as that admin.
    .mt-4
      %a.inline-flex.items-center.rounded.bg-sky-700.px-4.py-2.font-semibold.text-white.transition.hover:bg-sky-800{ href: random_record_path }
        Random Record

  %section
    %h2.text-xl.font-semibold Demo Queries
    .mt-4.grid.gap-4.md:grid-cols-2
      - @query_links.each do |link|
        %a.block.rounded.border.border-gray-200.p-4.transition.hover:border-sky-500.hover:bg-sky-50.dark:border-gray-700.dark:hover:border-sky-400.dark:hover:bg-gray-800{ href: demo_query_path(link[:id]) }
          %span.block.font-semibold= link[:title]
          %span.mt-1.block.text-sm.text-gray-600.dark:text-gray-300= link[:detail]

  %section
    %h2.text-xl.font-semibold Jaeger
    .mt-4.grid.gap-3.md:grid-cols-2
      - @jaeger_links.each do |title, href|
        %a.rounded.border.border-gray-200.p-3.font-medium.transition.hover:border-sky-500.hover:bg-sky-50.dark:border-gray-700.dark:hover:border-sky-400.dark:hover:bg-gray-800{ href: href }
          = title

  %section
    %h2.text-xl.font-semibold Local Tools
    .mt-4.grid.gap-3.md:grid-cols-2
      %a.rounded.border.border-gray-200.p-3.font-medium.transition.hover:border-sky-500.hover:bg-sky-50.dark:border-gray-700.dark:hover:border-sky-400.dark:hover:bg-gray-800{ href: '/graphiql' } GraphiQL
      %a.rounded.border.border-gray-200.p-3.font-medium.transition.hover:border-sky-500.hover:bg-sky-50.dark:border-gray-700.dark:hover:border-sky-400.dark:hover:bg-gray-800{ href: '/up' } Health Check
      %a.rounded.border.border-gray-200.p-3.font-medium.transition.hover:border-sky-500.hover:bg-sky-50.dark:border-gray-700.dark:hover:border-sky-400.dark:hover:bg-gray-800{ href: 'http://localhost:11150/' } Grafana
      %a.rounded.border.border-gray-200.p-3.font-medium.transition.hover:border-sky-500.hover:bg-sky-50.dark:border-gray-700.dark:hover:border-sky-400.dark:hover:bg-gray-800{ href: 'http://localhost:11170/' } Prometheus

  %section
    %h2.text-xl.font-semibold Experimental Account Pages
    %p.mt-2.text-sm.text-gray-600.dark:text-gray-300
      These exercise the heavier page expansion path and are useful when debugging downstream limits.
    .mt-4.grid.gap-3.md:grid-cols-2
      - @experimental_links.each do |title, href|
        %a.rounded.border.border-gray-200.p-3.font-medium.transition.hover:border-sky-500.hover:bg-sky-50.dark:border-gray-700.dark:hover:border-sky-400.dark:hover:bg-gray-800{ href: href }
          = title
